      {
         "id": "SECTION_tree",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Genealogical Tree\n\nThe figures listed in the **Sumerian King List** are detailed in the genealogical trees of *History Tracers* (<htcite0>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "70ba21f1-9da5-43ef-8f15-6a27ff96b678",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "Families",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "-1",
                        "day": "-1"
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<ul><li><htcite0>: We explored the first eight kings from the list, who ruled in the period before the flood.</li><li><htcite1>: We studied the list of kings of Kish, which includes two historically recognized kings: <i>Enmebaragesi</i> and <i>Aga</i>.</li><li><htcite2>: we explore various Mesopotamian epics, including the <i>Epic of Gilgamesh</i>. These remarkable works not only reflect the cultural and religious aspects of Sumerian civilization but also convey beliefs and narratives that continue to resonate to this day.</li><li><htcite3>: This text examines the First Dynasty of Ur as documented in the Sumerian King List and explores its relationship with the <i>Torah</i>.</li><li><htcite4>: One list mentions three kings who ruled for 356 years (Sumerian King List). Another list presents twelve kings who ruled for about 200 years (List of the Kings of Awan). Why does this discrepancy exist?</li> <li><htcite5>: According to the Sumerian King List, after three different cities had dominated, Kish regains control and is ruled for 3,195 years.</li> </ul>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "55e5065b-f9c7-4a51-a1bd-bf2df0f1fb2a",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
